st-ito - simple terminal
------------------------
st-ito is a simple virtual terminal emulator for X which sucks less.


Requirements
------------
In order to build st-ito you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (st-ito is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install st-ito (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running st-ito
--------------
If you did not install st-ito with make clean install, you must compile
the st-ito terminfo entry with the following command:

    tic -s st-ito.info

See the man page for additional details.

